1) Please include *.raw images in same directory as *.cpp files before executing the code.
*********************************************************************************
FILES INCLUDED AND FUNCTIONALTIES
---------------------------------
1)Image.cpp - Contains class Image and definitions of member functions.
2)Image.h - Contains definition of class Image.
3)Makefile - Makefile to run the code.
4)Problem1a_swirl.cpp - Geometrical modification to give swirl effect to the given image.
5)Problem1b_cube.cpp -  Perspective Transformation & Imaging Geometry.
6)Problem2a_dithering.cpp - Digital halftoning using dithering.
7)Problem2b_errDiffusion.cpp - Digital halftoning using error diffusion.
8)Problem2c_SCH.cpp - Scalar Color halftoning
9)Problem2d_VCH.cpp - Vector color halftoning
10)Problem3a_Nholes.cpp - Morphological processing to count number of holes.
11)Problem3a_numWhiteObj.cpp -Morphological processing to count number of white objects.
12)Problem3a_shrink.cpp - Morphological processing to count number of nails.
13)Problem3b_preprocessing.cpp - Preprocessing for horse image i.e. hole filling and smoothing.
14)Problem3b_skel.cpp - Morphological processing to skeletonize image. 
15)Problem3b_thin.cpp - Morphological processing to perform thinning on  horse image.
16)README - Readme file
17)HorseSm.raw - Image preprocessed using approach 1(described in report)
***************************************************************************************
STEPS TO RUN THE PROGRAM
------------------------
1) Unzip the folder and check if all files mentioned above are present in the folder.
2) Run the following commands from the folder which contains Makefile
   make clean
   make all
3) Raw output images will be created corresponding to all programs.
4) You should see self explanatory messages on screen.

********************************************************************************
DETAILED DESCRIPTION OF IMPLEMENTATION
-------------------------------------- 
Please look at Approach and Procedure section of report for detailed description of each program implementation.

Problem3b_skel.cpp
Problem3b_thin.cpp 
Above mentioned two files need raw image *HorseSm.raw which I have placed in folder.This image was generated by implementing approach 1 in matlab.
Approach 2 was implemented in C++.
