OUTPUT FILES
------------
1) kate_output.raw - swirl effect output
2) cube.raw - Problem 1b output
3) mandrill_output.raw - Problem2a output
4) mandrill_outputErr.raw - problem 2b output
5) Sailboat_sch.raw - Scalar color halftoning
6) Sailboat_vch.raw - Vector color halftoning
7) Horseshoe_output.raw - Shrinked horse shoe image
8) HorseshoeNwhite_output.raw - Shrinked horse hsoe after removing holes.
9) HorseshoeNhole_output.raw - Shrinked horse shoe after inverting the image.
10) Horse1_preproc.raw - preprocessed horse image
11) Horse1_thinoutput1.raw - thinning output for horse after preprocessing with approach 1
12) Horse1_thinoutput2.raw - thinning output for horse after preprocessing with approach 2
13) Horse1_outputNopre.raw - thinning output for horse without preprocessing.(comment out preproc code in Problem3b_thin.cpp) before genertaing this output.
14) Horse1_skeloutput1.raw - Skeleton output with approach 1 
14) Horse1_skeloutput2.raw - Skeleton output with approach 2.





























































